  M106 P1 S0
  
  ;Cool Down Tools
  G10 P0 S0 R0
  G10 P1 S0 R0
  G10 P2 S0 R0  git commit -m "Your commit message"
  G10 P3 S0 R0

  M140 S0       ; turn off bed heater
